{"tid":2009314,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"美國搖滾樂先驅 Little Richard 逝世，享年87歲","createTime":"2020-05-09T15:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T20:50:24.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b398ded950239ccfd5acbd2c995c689fe93eecae","tid":2009314,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"【兒子證死訊】「樂與怒之父」Little Richard逝世 享年87歲<br />\n20200509<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/yrHUzXk5swn4bTujPoR9PLiU4iE=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/TLYBYYQ6EGCG2BB6XS6SEAV6KU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FyrHUzXk5swn4bTujPoR9PLiU4iE%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FTLYBYYQ6EGCG2BB6XS6SEAV6KU.jpg&h=7e76ad12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「樂與怒之父」之稱的傳奇音樂人Little Richard今日逝世，享年87歲，他的兒子Danny Penniman向《滾石雜誌》證實死訊，但沒有透露Little Richard的死因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200509/large/1589033736_72a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200509%2Flarge%2F1589033736_72a3.jpg&h=2ce350a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLittle Richard於2002年獲頒美國全國有色人種協進會形象獎（NAACP Image Awards）。<br />\n<br />\nLittle Richard於50年代憑歌曲《Tutti Frutti》成名後，被認為是改變音樂世代的音樂人。Little Richard的音樂充滿咆哮聲、其憤怒的舞步與別樹一格的台上服飾，令他打響名堂。Little Richard名作包括《Long Tall Sally》、《Rip It Up》和《Good Golly Miss Molly》等，全部都是經典之作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/FM-cd8Vp0Y4tge4JybCR39airJs=/802x477/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XSYLPSDDXTXJZVPDBP62IVR22Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FFM-cd8Vp0Y4tge4JybCR39airJs%3D%2F802x477%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXSYLPSDDXTXJZVPDBP62IVR22Y.jpg&h=51febc3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許懷欣貼出睇Little Richard演唱會的票尾，悼念這位傳奇人物。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n許冠傑兒子許懷欣今晚在自己的IG貼出2002年Little Richard及另一位樂與怒的先驅Chuck Berry的演唱會票尾，並讚揚Little Richard是個傳奇人物，及指他對後代的音樂人影響深遠，他祝願Little Richard可以安息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/QSjUgpY025c2k8qO37tQCMn9i3M=/802x557/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/LRO53M3I6SKADPFUH6V3BCGEVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FQSjUgpY025c2k8qO37tQCMn9i3M%3D%2F802x557%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FLRO53M3I6SKADPFUH6V3BCGEVM.jpg&h=c0b84784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLittle Richard於2009年出席美國音樂人Fats Domino的致敬音樂會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200509/6OJWXEVHSCB5HGUQB7AOJZNIBA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2F6OJWXEVHSCB5HGUQB7AOJZNIBA%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=43477d4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200509%2F6OJWXEVHSCB5HGUQB7AOJZNIBA%2F&h=f734c7e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200509/6OJWXEVHSCB5HGUQB7AOJZNIBA/</a>"},{"pid":"e461612f38d4d93bf8fa12436e50ac7fec5a06bc","tid":2009314,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T20:50:24.000Z","msg":"Little Richard - Long Tall Sally/Tutti Frutti (1956)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LVIttmFAzek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLVIttmFAzek&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2Ffpf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=5bfd4c14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LVIttmFAzek</a>"}]}